  "name": "RPlog_An_Unscrupulous_Undertaking_Infiltration",
  "title": "An Unscrupulous Undertaking: Infiltration",
  "summary": "A Trandoshan strike team smuggles itself aboard the slaver transport Edean's Ferry by hiding inside a cargo container, passing a tense droid inspection by claiming the suspiciously light crate holds child slaves. Once the ship jumps to hyperspace, the warriors cut their way out and open fire on the droid sentries patrolling the cargo bay, deploying decoy noisemakers amid a brutal running firefight. Massive warehouse loader droids ambush and slaughter several of the infiltrators, forcing the survivors to split into teams and flee into the maintenance shafts. The assault-team leader Trrs'kal navigates the ship's ventilation system toward the bridge, losing comrades to a venting airlock along the way, while the support team battles an ancient HK droid in the reactor room. In the end the dying warrior Tahk'pa dons an environmental suit, manually shuts down the reactor from inside containment, and sacrifices himself, draining the ship's power and dropping it out of hyperspace.",
